The '''''Lianna Guard''''' was a [[Guardian-class light cruiser|''Guardian''-class light cruiser]] commanded by [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Lodrel]]. It was part of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] squadron present at the [[Battle of Nar Shaddaa (4 BBY)|Battle of Nar Shaddaa]] in [[4 BBY/Legends|4 BBY]]. The ship attempted to engage [[Salla Zend]]'s [[Rimrunner (Gymsnor-4)|''Rimrunner'']], but was quickly destroyed by the freighter's rear-firing [[Concussion missile/Legends|concussion missile]] launchers.

